```plantuml
@startuml kaleidot725_Draft

package "Emomemo App" {
    [ComposeMainActivity] as MainActivity
    [EmomemoApp] as AppClass

    package "Presentation Layer" {
        [ViewModels] as VMs
        [Compose UI] as UI
        [Navigation] as Nav
    }

    package "Domain Layer" {
        [Use Cases] as UseCases
        [Entities] as Entities
    }

    package "Data Layer" {
        [Repositories] as Repos
        [Room Database] as RoomDB
    }

    package "External Libraries" {
        [Orbit MVI] as MVI
        [Koin DI] as Koin
        [Coroutines] as Coroutines
    }
}

MainActivity --> UI : Hosts
AppClass --> Koin : Initializes
AppClass --> MVI : Uses

UI --> VMs : Observes state
VMs --> UseCases : Executes
UseCases --> Repos : Uses
Repos --> RoomDB : Accesses
RoomDB --> Entities : Stores

VMs --> MVI : Implements pattern
VMs --> Coroutines : Uses for async
UI --> Nav : Uses for navigation
Nav --> UI : Updates screens

@enduml
```